title: Wholesale Price of Douglas Fir Lumber for Washington
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables-- (1)--Original Data, 1913-1924 (2)--Original Data, 1922-1941. Data Are For No. 1 Common, 1"X8" F.O.B. Mill, Average Of Tuesdays' Quotations, List Price To Retail Dealers Less Cash Discount. Source: Bls Bulletins And "Wholesale Prices" Other Data Direct From Bls.
